# Optional code-to-doc sync rules.
# Format:
# <code path>[,<code path>...]|<doc path>[,<doc path>...]|<message>
# Add repository-specific extensions in .orch/rules/<target>/local.docsync.rules.
#
# Examples:
# app/internal/config,deploy/.env.runtime.example,deploy/.env.dev.example|docs/app/config.md|config changes must update docs
# app/internal/transport/httpapi,app/openapi|docs/app/api.md|api or contract changes must update docs
